 |url=http://www.pnas.org/content/105/32/11105.full
 |pmc=2516281
|bibcode = 2008PNAS..10511105C }}</ref><ref>
{{cite journal
 |author=Heaney ML, Gardner JR, Karasavvas N, ''et al.''
 |title=Vitamin C antagonizes the cytotoxic effects of antineoplastic drugs
 |journal=Cancer Res
 |volume=68
 |issue=19
 |pages=8031<U+2013>8
 |year=2008
 |month=October
 |pmid=18829561
 |doi=10.1158/0008-5472.CAN-08-1490
 |laysummary=http://well.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/10/01/vitamin-c-may-interfere-with-cancer-treatment/
 |laysource=New York Times
 |laydate=2008-10-01
}}</ref> Pauling has been criticised for making overbroad claims.<ref>
{{cite web
